Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(559.802,360)\frz17.39}系鞋带之歌 作曲及演唱
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.02,0:01:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚只是在找体育频道  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just looking for the sports channel, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.75,0:01:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要看下我的新鞋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,want to see my new shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.49,0:01:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞋子太棒了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are great, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.25,0:01:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看穿你脚上会是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what they look like on your feet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不看看穿我手上的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you rather see them on my hands?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.69,0:01:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还能把手套戴脚上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we can wear gloves on our feet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也能把帽子戴屁股上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and hats on our captain's quarters, too
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.13,0:01:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要坦白一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a confession to make
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道要怎么系鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:46.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to tie my shoelaces
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道你交了我这么个朋友有多幸运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know how lucky you are to have a friend like me?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着这个结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at this knot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有见过系得比这还要好的鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a more perfectly executed shoe-fastening bow?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,probably not
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打小就学会了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I learned when I was just a boy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.62,0:02:04.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很愿意倾囊相授
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:04.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm willing to pass on what I know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到那坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go sit over there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.47,0:02:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来让我这位老专家教你怎么系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and let an old pro show you how to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意看好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay close attention, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先要一只手拿一条鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you start by taking one lace per hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕个  个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,loop the, the
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定知道要怎么系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you know how to do it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.87,0:02:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星别顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, please
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系鞋带要安安静静心平气和才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shoe-tying requires peace and quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我刚讲到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, where was I?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你鞋带还是没系好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your shoes are still untied
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你是不想我教你系鞋带了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you don't want me to show you how to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.59,0:02:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会再插嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't interrupt anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系鞋带的第一条规矩是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The first rule of shoe-tying is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先从右脚系起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"always start with your right foot"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在课程即将正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now the lesson will officially begin
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.26,0:02:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.07,0:02:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.75,0:02:56.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:56.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  不闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, no more fooling around
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你不是干啥要来不及了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, aren't you late for something?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上厕所  你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The poop deck, you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能以后再来上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do this lesson later
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我会忘掉要怎么系鞋带了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I've forgotten how to tie my own shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自打我记事起  这鞋带就已经系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've been tied for as long as I can remember
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好  好好睡一晚上就会记起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll remember after a good night's sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No big deal
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我迟早都会记起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll remember sooner or later
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.42,0:03:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,read
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm read
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备
