Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让派大星看到我还没系好鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't let Patrick see I still haven't tied my shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你变矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're shorter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最近是不是在节食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you been dieting?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵就该有个海绵样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, a sponge has to look his spongiest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得上班去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I got to get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是躺这好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just lay here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡不会自己做好的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those patties aren't gonna cook themselves, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to make Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管鞋带系没系好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laces or no laces
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要站在这么一个地方就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just have to stand in this one spot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A perfect patty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,递过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand it over
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, I've got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你过来拿如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you come get it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你想得可真是美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee, SpongeBob, that's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就要让我做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And maybe I should cook the patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再然后洗盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and do the dishes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再然后穿方裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and wear square pants
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再然后住菠萝屋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and live in a pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要让你加入失业大军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while you wait in the unemployment line
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.94,0:05:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就马上把蟹黄堡递过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then bring that patty here now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming over
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把蟹黄堡递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm bringing the patty to you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes the patty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm walking
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带给章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over to Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把蟹黄堡给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you the patty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是为了饥饿的顾客们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the hungry customer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们把蟹黄堡吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so they can eat it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等带到你手里那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I give it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which is right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.95,0:06:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm over here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:25.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now move
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要慢慢动腿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just slowly move your leg
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Walk over there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再做一个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just make another
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.15,0:06:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:45.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me just
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.25,0:06:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么这么慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the holdup?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我心脏好像停跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think my heart just stopped
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob's fault
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's fault
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I failed
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的事业完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My career is over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, hat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1042,216)}蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  地板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, floor
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想  表示快乐的五个字母的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, a five-letter word for happiness
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.95,0:07:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Money"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是咱体验过最烂的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the worst service we've ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去海之霸好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:39.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,578)}老板
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  我们一定要走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, we are definitely out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱全都走出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me money walking out the door
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说这是什么意思  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是海绵宝宝的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SpongeBob's fault
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, get out here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出来点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再出来点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全身都给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the way, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What be the matter, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事我都该让你走甲板落海身亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ought to make you walk the plank for this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's just that I
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, I
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么怎么怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, I, I
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话快说  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out with it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘记怎么系鞋带了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot how to tie my shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这点事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会教我怎么系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you'll show me how?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不穿鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wear shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你能教我怎么系鞋带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you show me how to tie my shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是鳍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fins?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你能教我怎么系鞋带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you show me how to tie my shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是很想教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I would
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜我只是条鳗鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but, sadly I am only an eel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你们有谁可以教我怎么系鞋带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could any of you show me how to tie my laces?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你你你你你还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you, you, you, you, you or you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能教我怎么打个结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,show me how to tie a knot?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你能教我怎么打个小结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you show me how to tie a simple knot?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你能教我怎么系鞋带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you show me how to tie my shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你能教我怎么系鞋带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you show me how to tie my shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arr
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是幅画着人头的画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I be just a painting of a head
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.85,0:09:16.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁知道怎么打个结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:16.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't anybody know how to tie a knot?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人说到打结了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say knot?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.95,0:09:25.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.82,0:09:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是想打结啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you want to tie knots, do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很想  飞天魔鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, please, Mr. Flying Dutchman, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就找对飞天的魔鬼了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you've come to the right flying ghost, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.52,0:09:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你眼前看到的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're looking at
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.21,0:09:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三千年以来的打花结大赛冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the first place winner in the fancy knotting contest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the last 3,000 years
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别给我那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to not do that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别拿你大眼睛盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And stop staring at me with them big old eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.03,0:09:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快退后  看我打结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, stand back and watch me be knotty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蝴蝶脆饼结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pretzel knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双重钻石结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The double diamond knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方形结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The square knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨蟒结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The constrictor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消化道结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The gut knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,枕头结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pillow knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蝴蝶结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The butterfly knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's more
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,链环结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The monkey chain
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猴拳结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The monkey's fist
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猴子结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The monkey
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有个圆环结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one here's a loop knot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又叫做一拉即解方便结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,otherwise known as the poop loop
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poop?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系得太好了  飞天魔鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are great, Mr. Flying Dutchman, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你能教我怎么系鞋带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now can you show me how to tie my shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道要怎么系鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to tie me shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.32,0:10:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有五千多年没穿过鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't worn shoes for over 5,000 years
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过有时我倒喜欢给我尾巴穿只袜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But sometimes I like to wear this little sock
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over me ghostly tail
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在不行  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not now, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在没心情  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.72,0:11:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别烦我跟我没系好鞋带的鞋了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just leave me and my untied shoes alone, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have my attention
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然会系鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can tie shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hopping clams
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you learn how to do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想来学怎么系鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:50.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to learn how to tie your shoe
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这事非常的简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a very easy thing to do
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快坐下来  教你独门秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sit on down and I'll give you the scoop
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.88,0:11:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,256)}绕个圈
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就叫绕个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's called the loop-dee-loop
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一只手各拿一条鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to take a lace in each hand
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先往上绕再往下绕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go over and under again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕个圈再拉一拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You make a loop-dee-loop and pull
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的鞋子就能酷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your shoes are looking cool
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.19,0:12:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先往上往下  从左到右
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go over and back, left to right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕个圈再拉紧点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loop-dee-loop and you pull them tight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好比兔子耳朵或者蝴蝶结
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like bunny ears or a Christmas bow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,束紧之后就大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lace 'em up and you're ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕个圈再拉一拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You make a loop-dee-loop and pull
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的鞋子就能酷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your shoes are looking cool
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕个圈再拉一拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You make a loop-dee-loop and pull
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的鞋子就能酷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your shoes are looking cool
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.82,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(355,436)}章鱼哥的\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:46.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,410)\frz20.1}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,518)\frz17.45}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.43\pos(424,306)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(342,330)\frz17.84}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz17.84\pos(428,656)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  美好的春日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, beautiful springtime
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对多数人来说是嬉戏玩乐的好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A time of fun and frolic for most
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,506)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但对这位可怜懒虫就不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but not for this poor slob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多美好的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我却在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here I am
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.42,0:13:04.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,困在这么一座高胆固醇的监狱里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:04.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,trapped in a prison of high cholesterol
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会有人星期天来这的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one ever comes in on Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么蟹老板就不能放我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't Mr. Krabs just let us go home?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别按铃铛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, stop ringing this bell
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是测试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just testing it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人点餐我就会按铃铛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will ring the bell when there's an order
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's no customers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整天下来一个客人也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There hasn't been one all day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等多久也不会有人来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there isn't going to be any
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty coming up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.29,0:13:33.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:33.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像是我钱掉地上的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like me money dropping
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My babies
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚开  野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away, barbarian
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.94,0:13:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你们干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干干净净的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice clean money
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,soiled
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.74,0:13:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会照顾好你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸会把你们清干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Papa clean you up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clear the way
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't cry, little ones
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me dime
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's stuck
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快帮我一把  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to help me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须松手把硬币放了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to let go of the dime
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有十种不同的充分理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can think of ten good reasons
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不松手把硬币放了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to never let go of a dime, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定还有别的不放钱的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be another way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住我屁股  然后拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab me captain's quarters and heave
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me arms
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我住院期间  这里的事情交给你管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm putting you in charge of things around here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I'm gone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包在我身上  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can count on me, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保重  早日回归
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take care, hurry back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽快康复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get well soon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们深深挂念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in our thoughts
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多保持乐观  少点焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Takes more muscles to frown than to smile
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来干正事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's get down to business
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我作为新任经理的第一份公务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My first official act as new manager
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是让你升职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is to give you a promotion
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.77,0:15:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由你来负责收银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get to run the cash register
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来收银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cash register?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  谁要来做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, who's going to work the grill?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这也是所谓升职的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's part of the promotion I mentioned earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在要戴两顶帽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be wearing two hats now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由你负责接单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to take the orders
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再由你把餐点做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you're going to make them
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我一生最美好的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the best day of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是等等  如果我既收银又做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But wait, if I'm running the register and the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.85,0:15:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点特别重要的老板差事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got some very important boss-like errands to run
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:00.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘了教我怎么用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot to teach me how to use
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the cash register
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.36,0:16:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,按按钮  把钱放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You push the button and put the money inside
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  之后全靠你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're on your own
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信真的会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is really happening
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天  美好生活开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today I start living
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.52,0:16:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥啊  你这回表现可真出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squidward, you've really
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,outdone yourself this time
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.86,0:16:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松享受的美好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A beautiful day of relaxing and pampering
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还带薪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with pay
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我估计是有点愧对可怜的海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I do feel kind of bad for poor little SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留他一个人在那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all by his lonesome
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都会过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It will pass
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能就单纯站收银台那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's probably just standing at the register
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸上挂着傻傻的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with that stupid grin on his face
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我换两毛五的零钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could you give me change for a quarter?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘了教他怎么换零钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell him how to make change
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.80,0:17:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差事都办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All done with those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没办完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am not
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.92,0:17:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚想起来我要换一块钱零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just remembered I needed change for this dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要四个两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want four quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是十个一毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or ten dimes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是二十个半毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or 20 nickels
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是一百个一分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or 100 pennies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是一个两毛五三个一毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or one quarter, three dimes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七个半毛十个一分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seven nickels and ten pennies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者要是你能再拿五块钱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or, if you give me a five-dollar bill
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能换
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your options are
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.31,0:17:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My day off
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.38,0:17:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用想太多  放松就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no worries just relaxation
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是老板  这都是我应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the boss, I deserve this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正今天也不会来客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There won't be any customers today anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他估计会无聊地光站在那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll probably just stand there bored
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, bored
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Getting kind of bored
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.59,0:18:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在浪费我宝贵的放松时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am wasting valuable relaxing time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's what I'm doing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说真的  这种事可能性会有多大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, really, what are the odds?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝让蟹堡王失火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob setting the Krusty Krab on fire?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要服务吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, you dunce
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差事办得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are those errands going?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忙得很
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm very busy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢你的语气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like your tone
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.37,0:18:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.15,0:18:49.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干好你的活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do your jobs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  章鱼哥老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Mr. Tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.73,0:18:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  怪不得蟹老板让他管蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, no wonder Mr. Krabs put him in charge
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,re
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lax
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快失去你的蓝色光泽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're losing your bluish glow
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别老想这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying so much
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟着我念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, repeat after me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会回蟹堡王去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will not go back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要灭了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will destroy the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished --
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管我想的都什么乱七八糟的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter what sick fantasies run through my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也绝对不会回蟹堡王去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will not go back to that restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事  事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Errands, errands
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you finished those errands?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  我的事都没办完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am not finished with those errands
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且永远办不完  不要再问我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I never will be, so quit checking up on me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you're up to
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次你搞砸工作都要逼我回来看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forcing me to come back here every time you mess up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I haven't
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  也许你现在还没搞砸工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe you haven't messed up yet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但之后一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you will
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你真搞砸的那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And when you do
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定会逮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会逮到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  章鱼哥实在太敬业了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Squidward sure is a hard worker
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我戴着这两顶帽子的感觉好骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He makes me proud to wear these hats
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(432,628)}警戒线 禁止跨越
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.97,0:20:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要待在这享乐就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'll have to stay here and enjoy myself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不去想那个谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not even going to think about you-know-who
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那个什么地方做那个什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the you-know-what doing I-don't-care
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.85,0:21:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,relax
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让章鱼哥的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let Squid's day off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,begin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在监视我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's spying on me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查我是不是真在办差事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to see if I'm really doing errands
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他这样就擅离职守了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he left his post
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就终于能逮到他搞砸工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've finally caught him messing up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了  海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught you, Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.70,0:21:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,枝条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Branch
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹老板要我买的橡皮鸭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the rubber duck Mr. Krabs wanted me to get
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.62,0:21:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.72,0:21:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧蟹老板发现你是个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait till Mr. Krabs finds out you're a
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.97,0:21:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马桶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,toilet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就快疯了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're losing it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是再被这种想法冲昏头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I let this get to me again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后肯定就一路跑到蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just end up running down to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冲进大门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bursting through the front door
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,径直走向害我头疼的海绵宝宝面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,up to that yellow headache, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他就会说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he'll say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.07,0:21:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:21:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的事都办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you finished with those errands yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.78,0:22:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you're in here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要回蟹堡王去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's headed back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要先他一步到那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll beat him there
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put some clothes on
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真相要大白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The truth will be revealed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right on, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:27.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,588)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.19,0:22:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get plenty of rest
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.72,0:22:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是哪里不舒服了  就回来复诊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and if things don't seem right, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢医生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Doc
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.07,0:22:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你打败不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you can't beat me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:40.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,370)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.62,0:22:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught you now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't think I knew
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.08,0:22:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我窗外的枝条
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you were a stick outside my window
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.51,0:22:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者是我卫生间里的马桶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or the toilet in my bathroom
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后在我浴缸里  我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you were in my bathtub, and I
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.57,0:22:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.37,0:22:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.00,0:22:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再然后我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.00,0:22:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,swam
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.93,0:22:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游过下水道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down the drain
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先我一步回蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,beat me to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.57,0:23:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是不是表示
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.81,0:23:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的事都办完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am finished with those errands
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很想回来继续负责收银
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I want to take my place back at the cash register
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的很想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really do
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你可能会想把这个穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you might want to put these on
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, you know what?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.20,0:23:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  咱好像忘把关门标换成开门标了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, we forgot to switch the "Closed" sign to "Open"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,834)}关
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,834)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.51,0:23:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们本来可以休息一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost like we could have taken the whole day off
